  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 2cbaeec8dbe84e069925173ac3a6210b, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dlg_Ruins_GM_Angry
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::ElementalAlchemist.Dialogue.DialogueData
  _speaker: Grand Master
  _lines:
  - What are you doing? It is right there, everything, within your reach, and you hesitate?
  - Do you understand what I gave for this moment? Years. Everything I had. Every realm I sent you through was for this single fusion.
  - I made you a Master. I handed you the whole of my art. And now, at the very end, you let it come to nothing over some borrowed scruple.
  - Then we are finished, you and I. Keep your fragments. Keep your conscience. I will find another way, without you.
  - Do not come looking for me. You will not find me again.
